data.title: Cat Cow Stretch
instruction: Start on all fours, with knees under hips and wrists under shoulders
Take a deep breath in and as you do, lower your belly towards the floor and lift your chest and eyes towards the ceiling
Breathe out slowly through your mouth, round your spine towards the ceiling, tuck your tailbone under and drop your head
Breathe in and return to the starting position
Repeat this sequence for your intended sets

data.title: Push-up (wall)
instruction: Stand facing the wall, extend your arms in front of you and place your palms flat on the wall at shoulder height and shoulder-width apart
Bend your elbows and bring your body towards the wall
Press your palms into the wall to push your body back to the starting position
Keep your body in a straight line throughout the movement
Repeat the movement for the desired number of repetitions

data.title: Roll Pec Foam Rolling
instruction: Lie face down and position the foam roller underneath your chest
Position your hands above your head, at shoulder width
Roll up and down from your lower sternum to your armpits
Repeat the motions for a specific period or reps
Relax your body weight onto the foam roller for more intensity, if needed
